    "description": "一成不变，一如既往，日复一日。但或许还有更多东西，前提是你要观察得足够仔细……并且铭记于心。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回想你的周围</h2>带回这个美丽世界那被遗忘的奇观。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富游戏玩法</h2>在趣味盎然的游戏中重新发现迷人事物，例如星辰、花朵和树木。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >两种游戏模式</h2>在可选的第二种模式“Fragile Mode”中，直面这些奇观面对的诸多威胁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可用性</h2>通过多种设置调整游戏，使其贴合自己的喜好，比如随时无缝更改游戏难度，并且不会因此受到惩罚。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在手工精心打造的多样体验中，有许多奇妙事物可供探索<br></li><li> 休闲易上手的玩法<br></li><li> 两种游戏模式：Natural（悠闲治愈）/ 脆弱（有难度，需动脑）<br></li><li> 牵动人心的剪影风美术风格<br></li><li> 感情细腻、妙不可言的配乐<br></li><li> 1-2 小时左右的精悍游戏时间<br></li><li> 可使用键鼠、控制器或单纯使用鼠标游玩</li></ul>",
